Setup Instructions

Prerequisites
- Python 3.10+
- Qdrant Cloud account (free tier)
- Groq API key (free tier)
- Vapi account 

nstallation

```bash
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/akhileshnaidu20/legalai-hackblr-2026.git
cd legalai-hackblr-2026

# Create virtual environment
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate

# Install dependencies
pip install fastapi uvicorn python-dotenv groq qdrant-client sentence-transformers python-docx datasets

# Create .env file
cat > .env << EOF
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_key_here
QDRANT_URL=your_qdrant_url_here
QDRANT_API_KEY=your_qdrant_key_here
GOOGLE_API_KEY=your_gemini_key_here  # Optional, for fallback
VAPI_API_KEY=your_vapi_key_here
EOF

# Run data pipeline (one-time setup)
python scripts/step1_download_datasets.py
python scripts/step2_process_data.py
python scripts/step3_embed_and_upload.py
python scripts/step4_process_and_embed.py
```

### Running the Application

```bash
# Terminal 1: Backend
uvicorn backend.app.main:app --reload --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000

# Terminal 2: Frontend
cd frontend && python3 -m http.server 3000

# Terminal 3: Ngrok (for Vapi voice integration)
ngrok http 8000
```

Open http://localhost:3000 to use the application.

